  "decision_conditions": [
    "<p>The proposed development, by reason of poor layout, single aspect design and provision of basement living areas which would provide inadequate daylight and ventilation, would result in the provision of an unacceptable standard of residential accommodation. As such the proposed development is contrary to policy D6 (Housing Quality and Standards) of London Plan 2021 and policies LP1 (Design Quality and Local Character) and LP17 (Housing Design) of the Local Plan 2033 and the guidance contained within the Mayor of London's Housing SPG.<br></p>",
    "<p>The proposed development, by reason of not providing step free access, fails to provide a fully inclusive and accessible layout and is considered to provide an unsuitable and poor standard of accomodation for potential future residents, contrary to London Plan policies D5 (Inclusive Design), D7 (Accessible Housing), Local Plan 2033 policies LP1 (Design Quality) and L1P7 (Housing Design) and the Mayors (GLA) Housing SPG.&nbsp;<br></p>"
  ],
